title: NASUM - Grind Finale [2005] [Grindcore]
description:
Grind Finale is a two discs completion covering Nasum's entire career with songs from all the 15 studio recordings the band did between 1993 and 2004, with 21 songs previously unreleased publicly before.

It was originally going to be titled "Blueprint for Extinction", but since Mieszko died, the band felt that the word "extinction" made the whole title very inappropriate and started to think of a new title. The band started to think of a play on words with "Grind" somewhere in the title, and ended up with "Grind Finale" since it would be the final (bigger) release from Nasum.
